  "title": "Logistics Operation",
  "description": "<p>Logistics Operation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate between customers, suppliers, internal manufacturing department and forwarder to meet shipment schedules for both export and import shipments</li>\n  <li>Inventory management and maintenance of accurate stock records</li>\n  <li>Perform monthly/ yearly stock take and reporting (External / Internal)</li>\n  <li>Manage store operations, including receiving, inspecting, sorting, labeling, cleaning, packing, issuing goods and loading.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper packaging and unpacking protocols are followed.</li>\n  <li>Ensure warehouse storage capacity is kept at optimal levels</li>\n  <li>Uphold workplace safety and health practices.</li>\n  <li>Skip bin management</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc tasks by Management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirement</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess minimum Secondary Education and above.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 to 2 years of working experience in the related field is required.</li>\n  <li>Hardworking and independent.</li>\n  <li>Good Working Attitude</li>\n  <li>Team player and able to multi-task.</li>\n  <li>Require to have Staker/ Forklift License</li>\n  <li>All times compliance to the safety and security protocol/SOP of Genic Singapore Pte Ltd</li>\n  <li>Computer Literate – Proficiency in Microsoft Office e.g., Excel, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Benefit</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 working days</li>\n  <li>Woodlands</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefit</li>\n  <li>Friendly Working Environment</li>\n  <li>Work Life Balance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
